---
title: Sesame Pork Schnitzel & Garlic Rice with Japanese Aioli & Sweet Chilli Broccoli
description: We may be slightly off-key when it comes to karaoke, but our rendition of Japanese tonkatsu – crumbed and fried pork – hits
all the right notes. This star performer features a tasty pork schnitzel coated with panko and sesame seeds, accompanied by a
beautiful rainbow of veggies and tangy Japanese aioli.
